 or NULL if data not distributed\n\nparam data\n\nPointer to the array or its part in the current process\n\nparam shape\n\nExpected shape of the total array\n\ntype descr\n\nctypes.POINTER(c_int)\n\ntype data\n\nctypes.POINTER\n\ntype shape\n\n(int, int)\n\nreturn\n\nGathered array for the process (0,0), None for other processes\n```\n"]}, {"name": "scalapack4py.blacsdesc.ScaLAPACK4py.scatter_numpy", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "src", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "descr", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "dst", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Scatters numpy array over BLACS descriptor\n\\:param src:   Source array on a root process, must be None on non-root processes\n\\:param descr: Pointer to BLACS descriptor of the destination (`dst`) or NULL if data not distributed\n\\:param dst:   Pointer to the destination BLACS array\n\\:type src:    numpy.ndarray\n\\:type descr:  ctypes.POINTER(c_int)\n\\:type data:   ctypes.POINTER\n"]}, {"name": "scalapack4py.blacsdesc.ScaLAPACK4py.is_root", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "descr", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Returns True if descr is NULL or if the current process grid index is (0,0). False otherwise.\n\\:param descr: Pointer to BLACS descriptor or NULL if data not distributed\n\\:type descr:  ctypes.POINTER(c_int)\n\\:return:      True if descr is NULL or if the current process grid index is (0,0). False otherwise.\n"]}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}]}